Allied Supermarkets Inc said it filedwith the Securities and Exchange Commission a registrationstatement covering 240 mln dlrs of debt securities.    The company plans to offer 140 mln dlrs of seniorsubordinated discount debentures and 100 mln dlrs ofsubordinated debentures.    Proceeds will be used to finance Allied's acquisition ofVons Cos Inc.    Allied named Drexel Burnham Lambert Inc and Donaldson,Lufkin and Jenrette Securities Corp as co-underwriters of bothofferings. Reuter&#3;